
sequenceDiagram
  participant QN as Orchestrator
  participant MSH as Controller

  QN->>MSH: sig.config-update.{swarmId} (kind=plan, blocks[])
  MSH-->>QN: ack/ok
  QN->>MSH: sig.swarm-start.{swarmId} { runId, planId }
  MSH-->>QN: started
  MSH-->>QN: complete
  QN->>MSH: sig.swarm-stop.{swarmId} { runId }
